21 October 2010Minister Jeff Radebe to lead the JCPS Cluster and brief media on the signing of the Delivery Agreement on Outcome 3.Justice and Constitutional Development Minister, Jeff Radebe will lead the JCPS Cluster in briefing the media following the signing of the Delivery Agreement for Outcome 3: All people in South Africa are and feel safe.Focus of the cluster will be on the 8 specific areas of attention that must contribute towards the cluster objective to ensure that "All People in South Africa are and feel Safe". Media briefing:Date: Sunday, 24 October 2010 Time: 11:00 Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaNote: There will be a video link-up to the Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape TownRSVP by SMS to:David Masango Cell: 083 279 7520 (Pretoria)orTuso Zibula Cell: 072 127 1565 (Cape Town)For enquiries contact: Tlali Tlali Cell: 082 333 3880Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)